== UWANYIRIGIRA Marie Chantal ==
UWAMYIRIGIRA Marie Chantal,<ref>https://umuryango.rw/amakuru/mu-rwanda/article/uwanyirigira-marie-chantal-yatorewe-kuyobora-akarere-ka-burera</ref> ni umugore wavutse muri 1981, avukira mu karere ka Burera, akaba ari  muri muyobozi bw' inzego zibanze.

=== AMATEKA ===
UWANYIRIGIRA Marie Chantal, yavukiye mu murenge wa rusarabuye ho muri [[Akarere ka Burera|Burera,]] ninaho yize amashuri abanza, mugihe yari ageze mumashuri yi sumbuye yatangiye kwiga bimugoye kuko byari mugihe cy' umutekano muke. yakomeje kwiga aho mu mwaka wa 2010 niho yabonye impamyabumenyi y' icyiciro cya kabiri cya kaminuza muri KIE.

=== IMIRIMO YAKOZE ===
uyu mutegarugori yakoze imirimo itandukanye aho yabaye umuyobozi w' ishami ry' uburezi mu karere ka Burera ndetse mu mwaka wa 2019 yaje gutorerwa kuyobora akarere ka Burere nk' umunyamabanga nshingwabikorwa<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/politiki/amakuru/article/amateka-ya-uwanyirigira-utarigeze-atekereza-ko-yaba-meya</ref>


